Ways of showing greater balance are:
1) to reiterate consistently that the general populations are not responsible for the injustices & harm suffered on either side;
2) to fund the rebuilding of the Palestinian infrastructure & economy at least equally to the value of any military & other support to Israel, to publicly declare that it is doing so;
3) to state that defending the right of Palestinians to dignity & safety while under occupation is not incompatible with Israel's right to exist.
